analysis_result.summary: The rental agreement covers Flat No. 302, Rose Residency, in Baner, Pune, owned by Mr. Rajesh Sharma and leased to Ms. Priya Nair, a software engineer at Infosys Pune, with a permanent address in Kochi, Kerala. The monthly rent is ₹25,000, with an additional ₹2,000 charged for maintenance. A security deposit of ₹75,000 was paid by Ms. Nair via cheque number 128756 on March 1st, 20XX, ensuring her occupancy of the property.
